     This program is Freeware.
     
     I wouldn't dare to ask money for this. I made it in one day, and I made it
because I needed it. It doesn't worth any money at all. 

     But there are other shareware programs that are worthy, like Miami,
Voyager, MUI, MagicWB, etc... 
     Please consider sending the shareware fee to register those sharewares you
use all the time, or their authors will stop supporting the Amiga. Which is bad.
I know it's not painless, but some sharewares really worth their price (even
more than their price). I hate registering too, but I feel guilty if I use a
software a lot and don't register... So think about it!

     PS: this is not an ad for shareware registering. I just expressed my
